caption.p: Pathway enrichment of the DEGs. (A-F) Gene Set Enrichment Analysis of DEGs between the rapid recurrence and slow recurrence groups. The enriched terms including (A) positive regulation of biosynthetic process, (B) regulation of cell death, (C) positive regulation of gene expression, (D) small molecule metabolic process, (E) response to extracellular stimulus and (F) regulation of cell adhesion. DEGs, differentially expressed genes; GO, Gene Ontology.
